      private final void generateReport(File reportDestination)

      Generates a report and writes it to the given destination. Whether this destination denotes a folder or a file depends on the ReportFormat.

      Not all formats are defined for all report styles.

      Parameters:
      reportDestination - The destination for the generated report.
      See Also:

    • initialize

      private final boolean initialize(String[] args) throws IOException, SQLException
      Initialises the application.
      Parameters:
      args - The command line arguments.
      Returns:
      true if the initialisation was successful and the application may proceed, false if it failed and the application needs to terminate.
      Throws:
      IOException - An I/O issue occurred.
      SQLException - A problem occurred when initialising the database.
